<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>The Empire — Dashboard</title>
  <style>
    :root { 
      --bg:#0b0e12; 
      --panel:#121624; 
      --text:#e8eaed; 
      --muted:#b6b9c2; 
      --gold:#f1c40f; 
      --shadow:rgba(0,0,0,.5); 
    }
    * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
    body {
      background:var(--bg); color:var(--text);
      font-family: system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;
      min-height:100vh; display:flex; flex-direction:column;
    }
    header {
      text-align:center; padding:18px;
    }
    .banner {
      max-width: 640px; width:100%;
      border-radius:12px; box-shadow:0 12px 32px var(--shadow);
    }
    .banner-caption {
      margin-top:10px;
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.3rem);
      font-weight:700;
      color: var(--gold);
      text-align:center;
      letter-spacing:.03em;
    }
    main {
      flex:1;
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
      gap:18px; padding:20px;
    }
    .card {
      background:var(--panel);
      padding:20px; border-radius:12px;
      box-shadow:0 6px 18px var(--shadow);
    }
    .card h2 { font-size:1.1rem; margin-bottom:8px; }
    .card p { color:var(--muted); font-size:.95rem; }
    footer {
      padding:14px; text-align:center; font-size:.9rem;
      color:var(--muted); background:#0e1017;
    }
  </style>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/empire-style.css">
<script src="/assets/js/empire-frame.js" defer></script>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/empire-style.css">
<script src="/assets/js/empire-frame.js" defer></script>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
         class="banner"/>
    <div class="banner-caption">⚔️ The Empire Command Interface ⚔️</div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Today's Orders</h2>
      <p>Status overview and quick actions.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Top Offers</h2>
      <p>What’s converting right now across regions.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Signals</h2>
      <p>Alerts, anomalies, and opportunities.</p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>Commanding the Future of Affiliate Marketing</footer>
</body>
</html>
